</quote>
<pc>”</pc>仁宗善之<pc>，</pc>命知<placeName>隴州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>擢<placeName>秦鳳路</placeName>馬步軍副總管<pc>。</pc>詔陝西增城壘<pc>、</pc>器械<pc>，</pc>
